title: Did President Trump win the US missile hit Syria?
subtitle: On the Internet, it was alleged that President Trump owned a stockpile in Rython and thus benefited from an American Tomahuk rocket strike on a Syrian airbase in April 2017.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: President Trump has a stockpile in Raytheon and has directly benefited from the use of Tomahawk missiles in an American attack in April 2017 on a Syrian airbase.
